        "timestamp": "2020-01-16 13:48:34.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nVijay, do you concur with Jessica's new requirement?  None of the dcaegen2 SONAR jobs do this, currently, and, looking at a sampling of ONAP projects that have done this, many of them appear in sonar.onap.org, but haven't run for months.\n\nI would think this would be an ONAP wide change, done all at once, so everyone would know about it and know where to go to find the results (assuming they are going somewhere other than sonar.onap.org)\n\nI would think that, at the very least, we'd want to move all of dcaegen2 over, at once, rather than just this one job, and that, maybe, it should be done in one place.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
