          "username": "jwagantall"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-01-16 14:10:18.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+2\n\nI'm ok either way, as long as we migrate soon :)",
